display_long_description:
Locked At Level One invites you into the mysterious world of 'Elevore Earth', the most realistic RPG ever created. You play as Slayer, a level one playtester, but soon realize you're unable to level up. NPCs have gone into hiding, and your journey to uncover the game's dark truth begins.

The game is currently in Early Access, with the first chapter fully playable and featuring 10 levels. Whether you prefer a cozy experience to enjoy the rich atmosphere or crave chaos and destruction, the choice is yours. Engage in combat with anyone, interact with a fully destructible environment, and choose your allies or enemies wisely—your actions have consequences. Be too chaotic, and a bounty may be placed on your head.

A full story, based on an original book written by the developer, is coming soon, promising an epic tale to unfold as the game continues to develop.
